N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 341.16 - Agenda

State Regulations

The agenda for each regularly scheduled or special
meeting of the student assembly will be established according to procedures
outlined in the bylaws. All meetings of the student assembly shall include the
opportunity for the chancellor or designee to address the
membership. Notes
